WHEN SETTING UP PROJECT FROM SCRATCH

-- Setup

## init project after navigating to desired location (I do ./Downloads or ./Documents)
react-native init Venue


-- Navigation

## add react-navigation via yarn in project folder
yarn add react-navigation

## add gestures via yarn in project folder
yarn add react-native-gesture-handler

## link the native dependencies of gesture handler in project folder
react-native link react-native-gesture-handler

-- Linear gradient

## add gradient via yarn in project folder
yarn add react-native-linear-gradient --save

## link the native dependencies of gradient in project folder
react-native link react-native-linear-gradient


-- Maps

See https://github.com/react-native-community/react-native-maps/blob/master/docs/installation.md
